
@startuml

' Aircraft and related classes
class Aircraft {
  - name: String
  - type: String
  - yearOfManufacture: int
  - nextInspectionDate: Date
}

class PassengerAircraft {
  - numberOfSeats: int
}

class SeatCategory {
  - designation: String
  - hasEntertainment: boolean
  - numberOfSeats: int
}

class Flight {
  - flightNumber: String
  - date: Date
  - departureAirport: Airport
  - destinationAirport: Airport
}

class Ticket {
  - ticketNumber: String
  - price: double
  - upgradeDesired: boolean
}

class Passenger {
  - name: String
  - passportNumber: String
}

class Airline {
  - name: String
}

class FlightAttendant {
  - name: String
  - employmentDate: Date
  - isChiefSteward: boolean
}

class Pilot {
  - name: String
  - employmentDate: Date
  - license: String
}

class Airport {
  - name: String
  - address: String
  - numberOfRunways: int
}

' Inheritance
PassengerAircraft --|> Aircraft

' Associations
Aircraft "1" --> "0..*" Flight : performs
Flight "1" --> "1" Aircraft : performed by
Flight "1" --> "1" DepartureAirport : departs from
Flight "1" --> "1" DestinationAirport : arrives at
DepartureAirport <|-- Airport
DestinationAirport <|-- Airport

Flight "1" --> "0..*" Ticket : has
Ticket "1" --> "1" Passenger : belongs to
Ticket "1" --> "1" SeatCategory : for category
SeatCategory "1" --> "1" PassengerAircraft : belongs to

PassengerAircraft "1" --> "0..*" SeatCategory : has
PassengerAircraft "1" --> "1" Aircraft : is a

Aircraft "0..1" --> "1" Airline : belongs to
Airline "1" --> "0..*" Aircraft : owns

Airline "1" --> "0..*" FlightAttendant : employs
Airline "1" --> "0..*" Pilot : employs

Flight "1" --> "1..*" FlightAttendant : crew members
Flight "1" --> "1" Captain : pilot
Flight "1" --> "0..2" CoPilot : co-pilots
Captain <|-- Pilot
CoPilot <|-- Pilot

' Notes for roles
note right of FlightAttendant
  Includes Chief Steward or Stewardess
end note

@enduml

---

### ✅ Explanation of Key Relationships:
- **Inheritance**: `PassengerAircraft` inherits from `Aircraft`.
- **Associations**:
  - An `Aircraft` can perform multiple `Flights`.
  - A `Flight` has one `Aircraft`, one `DepartureAirport`, and one `DestinationAirport`.
  - Each `Flight` has many `Tickets`.
  - Each `Ticket` is associated with a `Passenger` and a `SeatCategory`.
  - A `PassengerAircraft` has multiple `SeatCategory` types.
  - An `Airline` may own multiple `Aircraft` and employ multiple `Pilots` and `FlightAttendants`.
  - A `Flight` is staffed by one `Captain` (a `Pilot`) and optionally up to two `CoPilots`.

